title: Nsasoft SpotAuditor 4.0.7 [ak]
description:
Nsasoft SpotAuditor 4.0.7

SpotAuditor is a software that reveals passwords saved in Internet Explorer.SpotAuditor reveals passwords saved in Internet Explorer, recovers ICQ, Far ftp, Dial up, Outlook and MSN messenger passwords, IE Auto Complete Fields. It is a program for viewing and cleaning the secret data stored by Internet Explorer.SpotAuditor allows deletion of unwanted entries from the system protected storage. The program also explores Outlook Accounts, Visited URLs, Installed Programs and Start Run Programs on a local machine or remote computers. SpotAuditor allows to clear Internet Explorer history, delete cookies and temporary internet files. SpotAuditor is a software that reveals passwords saved in Internet Explorer.

You can recover and restore any lost or forgotten password ever entered in Internet Explorer. If you forget your passwords or need to access some passwords or confidential information stored in your computer, SpotAuditor can really help you to do it.
All the mentioned features are provided with a user friendly graphical interface.
